Code 
import numpy as np
from sklearn.ensemble import RandomForestClassifier
from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split, StratifiedKFold, GridSearchCV, cross_val_score
from sklearn.metrics import roc_auc_score
from sklearn.preprocessing import LabelEncoder

x_train['환불금액'] = x_train['환불금액'].fillna(x_train['환불금액'].mean())
x_train['실제구매액'] = x_train['총구매액'] - x_train['환불금액']

x_test['환불금액'] = x_test['환불금액'].fillna(x_test['환불금액'].mean())
x_test['실제구매액'] = x_test['총구매액'] - x_test['환불금액']

qual_col = ['주구매상품', '주구매지점']

for col in qual_col :
    le = LabelEncoder()
    x_train[col] = le.fit_transform(x_train[col])
    x_test[col] = le.transform(x_test[col])
Code 
skf = StratifiedKFold(n_splits = 5, shuffle = True, random_state = 42)
x_data, y_data = x_train.drop(columns = 'cust_id'), y_train['gender']

rf_clf = RandomForestClassifier(random_state = 42)

param_grid = {'n_estimators' : [100, 200, 500],
              'max_depth' : [5, 10, 20],
              'max_leaf_nodes' : [5, 10],
              'criterion' : ['entropy', 'gini']}


grid_search = GridSearchCV(rf_clf, param_grid = param_grid, cv = skf, scoring = 'roc_auc')
grid_search.fit(x_data, y_data)

print('Best Parameters : ', grid_search.best_params_)
print('Best Score : ', round(grid_search.best_score_, 4))
Best Parameters :  {'criterion': 'gini', 'max_depth': 5, 'max_leaf_nodes': 10, 'n_estimators': 100}
Best Score :  0.657
Code 
valid_rocauc = []
cnt = 1
skf = StratifiedKFold(n_splits = 5, shuffle = True, random_state = 42)
x_data, y_data = x_train.drop(columns = 'cust_id'), y_train['gender']

for train_idx, valid_idx in skf.split(x_data, y_data) :
    x_train, y_train = x_data.iloc[train_idx], y_data.iloc[train_idx]
    x_valid, y_valid = x_data.iloc[valid_idx], y_data.iloc[valid_idx]
    
    rf_clf = RandomForestClassifier(**grid_search.best_params_, random_state = 42)
    rf_clf.fit(x_train, y_train)
    
    valid_score = roc_auc_score(rf_clf.predict(x_valid), y_valid)
    print(f'{cnt}번째 Fold ROC-AUC Score : {valid_score}')
    valid_rocauc.append(valid_score)
    cnt += 1

print(f'모델 평균 ROC-AUC Score : {np.array(valid_rocauc).mean()}')
1번째 Fold ROC-AUC Score : 0.6360665478312537
2번째 Fold ROC-AUC Score : 0.6384848484848484
3번째 Fold ROC-AUC Score : 0.6005844645550528
4번째 Fold ROC-AUC Score : 0.5908670196736837
5번째 Fold ROC-AUC Score : 0.5769110275689223
모델 평균 ROC-AUC Score : 0.6085827816227523
